reviewText: With all-star cast It should've been better !
not worth my time and not enough available classics that i searched for such as the executioners of death or five deadly venoms or kid with the golden arm or any bruce lee classic
These movies were ok, but they weren't my kind of kung fu movies, but if you like true old school then you will like these.
After seeing the 1st in this series of classic kung fu dvd's I thought that kung fu 2 was equally as good-original and a great bargain to get two features for the price of one.
